      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "text": "Requirements agent translates intent into 01-requirements.md.\nChallenger review returns challenge-findings.json.\nOrchestrator presents both to the user before architecture starts.",
      "fontSize": 17,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "originalText": "Requirements agent translates intent into 01-requirements.md.\nChallenger review returns challenge-findings.json.\nOrchestrator presents both to the user before architecture starts.",
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "specialist-2-box",
      "type": "rectangle",
      "x": 960,
      "y": 397,
      "width": 660,
      "height": 130,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#22c55e",
      "backgroundColor": "#c3fae8",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "roundness": {
        "type": 3
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "specialist-2-text",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 995,
      "y": 421,
      "width": 590,
      "height": 72,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#14532d",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "text": "Architect evaluates WAF tradeoffs and cost posture.\nThe cost-estimate-subagent handles pricing lookups.\nOutputs: 02-assessment.md, 03-cost-estimate.md, plus challenge findings.",
      "fontSize": 17,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "originalText": "Architect evaluates WAF tradeoffs and cost posture.\nThe cost-estimate-subagent handles pricing lookups.\nOutputs: 02-assessment.md, 03-cost-estimate.md, plus challenge findings.",
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "specialist-3-box",
      "type": "rectangle",
      "x": 960,
      "y": 582,
      "width": 660,
      "height": 130,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#22c55e",
      "backgroundColor": "#c3fae8",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "roundness": {
        "type": 3
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "specialist-3-text",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 995,
      "y": 606,
      "width": 590,
      "height": 72,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#14532d",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "text": "The Bicep or Terraform planner creates the implementation plan.\nThe governance-discovery-subagent pulls Azure Policy constraints.\nOutputs: 04-plan.md, governance constraints, and challenge findings.",
      "fontSize": 17,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "originalText": "The Bicep or Terraform planner creates the implementation plan.\nThe governance-discovery-subagent pulls Azure Policy constraints.\nOutputs: 04-plan.md, governance constraints, and challenge findings.",
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "specialist-4-box",
      "type": "rectangle",
      "x": 960,
      "y": 775,
      "width": 660,
      "height": 122,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#22c55e",
      "backgroundColor": "#c3fae8",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "roundness": {
        "type": 3
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "specialist-4-text",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 995,
      "y": 798,
      "width": 590,
      "height": 72,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#14532d",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "text": "IaC codegen produces AVM-first templates in infra/bicep/{project}\nor infra/terraform/{project}. Validation either passes for approval\nor loops back for revision with feedback.",
      "fontSize": 17,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "originalText": "IaC codegen produces AVM-first templates in infra/bicep/{project}\nor infra/terraform/{project}. Validation either passes for approval\nor loops back for revision with feedback.",
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "specialist-5-box",
      "type": "rectangle",
      "x": 960,
      "y": 997,
      "width": 660,
      "height": 130,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#22c55e",
      "backgroundColor": "#c3fae8",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "roundness": {
        "type": 3
      }
    },
    {
