      "type": "text",
      "x": 995,
      "y": 1021,
      "width": 590,
      "height": 72,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#14532d",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "text": "Deploy executes only after a what-if or terraform plan preview.\nThe user verifies the live deployment before the workflow continues.\nOutput: 06-deployment-summary.md.",
      "fontSize": 17,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "originalText": "Deploy executes only after a what-if or terraform plan preview.\nThe user verifies the live deployment before the workflow continues.\nOutput: 06-deployment-summary.md.",
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
